## 8. Core User Journeys

### Visitor to customer

1. Visitor lands on premium marketing site
2. Browses services / AI training / pricing
3. Requests consultation or signs up
4. Verifies with email OTP or phone OTP
5. Creates account profile
6. Purchases plan or requests custom quote
7. Completes payment
8. Gets dashboard access
9. Tracks service progress / training / invoices / support

### Admin operations

1. Admin reviews lead pipeline
2. Qualifies inquiry
3. Creates service proposal or links plan
4. Confirms payment / onboarding
5. Assigns delivery milestones or training access
6. Monitors user activity, logins, OTP attempts, and tickets
7. Reviews analytics and exports reports

